Scanner input = new Scanner(System.in);
int mat1[][]={{1,2},{5,3}};
int mat2[][]={{2,3},{4,1}};
int mat_sum[][]=new int[2][2];
int len=mat1.length;
for(int i=0;i<len;i++)
{
 for(int j=0;j<len;j++)
 {
 mat_sum[i][j]=mat1[i][j]+mat2[i][j];
 System.out.print(mat_sum[i][j]+"\t");
 }
 System.out.println();

Output:

Sample Input:
Mat1 = 1 2
       5 3
Mat2 = 2 3
       4 1
Sample Output:
Mat Sum = 3 5
          9 4
